It starts out by sowing in the morning, sowing in the evening, right?

00:23:04.059 --> 00:23:07.899
And the song starts that way because you're not going to bring in the sheaves

00:23:07.899 --> 00:23:09.179
if you're not first sowing.

00:23:09.179 --> 00:23:11.419
It makes sense, right?

00:23:11.419 --> 00:23:14.779
And the songwriter understood something about agriculture

00:23:14.779 --> 00:23:17.899
is using that analogy in the song, and so we understand.

00:23:17.899 --> 00:23:21.579
And I was convicted as I was reading that song earlier in the day,

00:23:21.579 --> 00:23:22.779
and I mentioned it on Sunday.

00:23:22.779 --> 00:23:25.579
I was reading, I was sitting here on the pulpit as I prayed in the morning,

00:23:25.579 --> 00:23:28.219
and as I was reading through the words of the song, I was convicted,

00:23:28.219 --> 00:23:29.979
and I asked myself this question,

00:23:29.979 --> 00:23:33.419
when is the last time I even tried to share the gospel with someone?

00:23:34.379 --> 00:23:39.099
If that's what our purpose is, we have to ask ourselves the question,

00:23:39.099 --> 00:23:40.459
so sometimes we ask the question,

00:23:40.459 --> 00:23:43.579
when's the last time you led somebody to Christ?

00:23:43.579 --> 00:23:48.539
One of the difficulties with that question is I don't have a control over that

00:23:48.539 --> 00:23:53.099
because the Bible says that some plant some water, but God gives the increase.

00:23:53.099 --> 00:23:55.499
So I have to leave that part in God's hands.

00:23:55.499 --> 00:23:59.659
I can't control whether or not I could lead somebody to Christ,

00:23:59.659 --> 00:24:02.859
but the reality is that I better be sharing the gospel.

00:24:03.099 --> 00:24:06.139
Now, I can't force anyone to listen to the gospel,

00:24:06.859 --> 00:24:09.899
but am I even trying to share the gospel?

00:24:09.899 --> 00:24:12.299
Am I trying to sow the seed?

00:24:12.299 --> 00:24:14.619
The folks that I come in contact with,

00:24:14.619 --> 00:24:18.380
the people that I rub shoulders with throughout the week,

00:24:19.819 --> 00:24:22.220
are those people, do they know that I'm a Christian?

00:24:22.220 --> 00:24:25.099
